---
title: Cheesy Beef Rissoles & Burger Sauce with Cucumber Slaw & Herbed Potato Chunks
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner winner, but when you cover them in gooey cheese, they’re even harder to refuse! This
colourful plate also gets a serve of garlic infused potatoes and an irresistible slaw to really win over your stomach.

